        <div class="hr"></div>

        <details>
          <summary>What ‚Äú*stars*‚Äù mean</summary>
          <div class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">
            Words wrapped in <span class="mono">*</span>like this<span class="mono">*</span> will appear <em>italicized</em>.
